{"tid":2215872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【最強文宣！】「新疆數據計畫」上線！一站式提供有關新疆受壓迫民族嘅資料","createTime":"2020-09-24T09:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T17:49:07.000Z","uid":138409,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8f093407c642496e564beb5fc9445ffce1c76ef7","tid":2215872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"以後凡係有新疆相關嘅新聞，就comment呢條link<br />\n<a href=\"https://xjdp.aspi.org.au/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxjdp.aspi.org.au%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=a65db852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xjdp.aspi.org.au/</a><br />\n<br />\n各位同我推爆條tweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Nrg8000/status/1308950444388089857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNrg8000%2Fstatus%2F1308950444388089857&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=5d48ce65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNrg8000%2Fstatus%2F1308950444388089857&h=b32806ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Nrg8000/status/1308950444388089857</a><br />\n<br />\n個網站由澳洲戰略政策中心同埋唔同嘅專家合作整出黎<br />\n集合有關維吾爾人/新疆非漢族民族人權狀況嘅資料<br />\n議題圍繞大規模拘禁、監控、強迫勞役及供應鏈、「再教育」計畫、摧毀文化等議題<br />\n<br />\n網站資料來自 開源數據，例如衛星影像、中國政府檔案、官方數據以及一系列權威報告及學術研究。<br />\n<br />\n有關集中營嘅介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://xjdp.aspi.org.au/explainers/exploring-xinjiangs-detention-facilities/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxjdp.aspi.org.au%2Fexplainers%2Fexploring-xinjiangs-detention-facilities%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=f5826dff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xjdp.aspi.org.au/explainers/exploring-xinjiangs-detention-facilities/</a><br />\n<br />\n有關再教育、強制勞動、監控等介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://xjdp.aspi.org.au/explainers/uyghurs-for-sale/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxjdp.aspi.org.au%2Fexplainers%2Fuyghurs-for-sale%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=06511c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xjdp.aspi.org.au/explainers/uyghurs-for-sale/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">集中營、被摧毀之古蹟及清真寺 地圖</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://xjdp.aspi.org.au/map/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxjdp.aspi.org.au%2Fmap%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=3591c03e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xjdp.aspi.org.au/map/</a>"},{"pid":"13954abde1fa1c71d2999f4e38cf786ac7fa1168","tid":2215872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9d6426b21f9a44919269cb52398d06dafab7ded","tid":2215872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"508f5104be650dafd7fc326d8534a9cc43896984","tid":2215872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7d87908b4d858fa6007b02fbfea28fc286ba6a6e","tid":2215872,"uid":347237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"4dc14ac7b29b273631b0ff2b6dcd683c9b0b0b30","tid":2215872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"25e3b97152098640287b8223197f7e5d09612a52","tid":2215872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"096a428e53bbde3096b548f26b3dc63b1befc39b","tid":2215872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:41:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c967c8740849831669bcd517ecf98a58d71b7ffd","tid":2215872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7cad48a8b7e2d19a0c936ec92e370